{"tid":1994969,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【51黃金周撐黃店】騎劫五一黃金周，令五一變成禁語","createTime":"2020-04-30T01:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T03:27:49.000Z","uid":145118,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa321eb8cb803d6f0ba38f46f1f9f995bfa4227e","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5QkqTpe1cvk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5QkqTpe1cvk&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw3T1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=89df7c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5QkqTpe1cvk</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情打擊消費市道，民間記者會及終極黃藍地圖等發起「黃金周支援黃店計劃」，由今日至5月3日提供各式優惠，至昨晚已有逾1,700間商舖及網店參與，反應踴躍，市民到黃店消費，有助壯大黃色經濟圈。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有商戶指顧客高舉「五」、「一」手勢或高叫口號等，便可獲得優惠。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>市民要高舉五一手勢</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n疫情之下，民間記者會、終極黃藍地圖、香港良心Guide及香城online發起「黃金周支援黃店計劃」，發起黃店今日起至5月3日長假期間為顧客提供不同優惠，計劃至昨晚10時已有逾1,700間商舖及網店參與，反應熱烈，商舖種類橫跨美容及健康、髮型、服裝、婚禮、珠寶鐘錶、食店、遊戲、盆栽及種植、飲食零售和電子產品等多個範疇。<br />\n<br />\n商店提供的優惠各有不同，主要提供折扣和購物免運費，或向顧客贈送消毒搓手液，亦有要商戶會要求市民高舉「五」、「一」手勢，或高叫口號等，便可獲得優惠。市民可登上香港良心Guide搜索黃店，或到優惠網頁了解詳情。<br />\n<br />\n計劃文宣指，要打破港人對黃金周有大量內地人消費，只有奢侈品商店受益的印象，聲言計劃要改變現象，振興黃色經濟圈，更稱「騎劫五一黃金周，令五一變成禁語」，並呼籲港人光顧時可打卡「#五一黃金周」，並領取宣傳貼紙，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>鼓勵更多人參與屬於香港人的黃金周</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n記者鍾雅宜、曾偉龍<br />\n<br />\nSource <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200430&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20909843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200430%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20909843&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw3T1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=65f983b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200430%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20909843&h=9c37a0c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200430&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20909843</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408c71627a3fb4e9361412da20f70e174cbcf5a6","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c2984b72c9efbe0b52cc6348147afb91d4fd093f","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:03:41.000Z","msg":"唔見人"},{"pid":"577d8e2228efd3cfe8df0e8cd6f367513c646703","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:03:54.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"dbd94a8d0661b2f6babebe8d0f427c29617d86a7","tid":1994969,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b865c21733b29f86300ed09372649d3393dbd823","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"打死人"},{"pid":"9a94f055741d961f44ea97ca8f18d3c32bdc8de5","tid":1994969,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:06:48.000Z","msg":"香港人嘅五一黃金週"},{"pid":"d0bf0710ade42b1d265e554a4a416a9b15ee8611","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:08:01.000Z","msg":"101"},{"pid":"415aa267dbbefda7c851babd2f946465138c4c18","tid":1994969,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:08:52.000Z","msg":"好似好多嘢買，好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810301821dcda01d156440e18956aafa5b265565","tid":1994969,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"槍殺人"},{"pid":"654c7c185a248b48277121790acd45d9ca530c48"